column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid,p.ra,p.dec, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, pz.z as photoredshift,  GN.distance FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN PhotoZ AS pz ON pz.objid = p.objid JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,+#, #) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID WHERE  s.class = GALAXY
